programme.title: Sandringham: A Royal Residence - Finale
programme.desc: A documentary series that explores the intimate and multifaceted history of the British royal familys favorite private residence. Throughout the episodes, it is revealed how Sandringham has been a part of pivotal moments in the monarchy: from royal Christmases to historic speeches, from wartime to discreet romances. Through rare archives, expert testimony, and visits to the estates lesser-known spaces, the series showcases the daily life, traditions, and transformations of this royal retreat. More than just a palace, Sandringham emerges as a crucial stage for the family, political, and emotional life of Windsor.Saturday at 9:40PM
